1. Scope and Principles
Include 3–5 sentences:

This standard applies to all servers, containers, endpoints, cloud accounts, databases, and network devices in production, staging, and corporate environments.

All systems must follow a documented, approved baseline configuration before going live.

Changes to baselines or individual configurations must go through change management and be tracked.

